data.description: Stunning three-story townhome boasting a wealth of desirable features. This exceptional end unit is situated on a tranquil cul-de-sac, offering a rare sense of privacy. Step inside the welcoming foyer adorned with exquisite hardwood floors, which gracefully extend down the hall, leading to the fourth bedroom or ideal home office space. Continuing down the hall, you'll find access to the impressive 45-foot-deep garage, providing ample space for two vehicles and an abundance of storage options. The garage conveniently opens to a charming patio area that leads to a private backyard oasis.Moving upstairs to the main living area, you'll be greeted by beautiful hardwood flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the living room, dining area, kitchen, and the hallway leading to the masterbedroom. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, including a 25-cubic-foot refrigerator, a gas range, microwave, and an upgraded dishwasher. Granite countertops complimented by an elegant tile backsplash add a touch of sophistication to this culinary haven. The master bedroom offers a retreat-like ambiance, complete with a generous walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom featuring a relaxing garden tub and a separate shower, both adorned with tasteful tile surrounds. The third floor boasts two spacious bedrooms, connected by a convenient Jack and Jill bathroom, ensuring comfort and convenience for all. This townhome is a true gem, offering a harmonious blend of style, functionality, and luxury. Right in the heart of North Mount Pleasant, you are close to shopping, dining, beaches, and excellent schools. This gem won't last long!  A $2,100 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender.  This credit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.
